title: INSV Kaundinya's maiden voyage revives India's ancient sea legacy
description: INSV Kaundinya, the Indian Navy's traditionally built stitched sailing vessel, began its maiden voyage from Porbandar to Muscat. The historic expedition aims to revive India's ancient maritime heritage and strengthen ties with Oman.
